com.ephesoft.dcma.kvextraction

Class KeyValueExtraction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ephesoft.dcma.kvextraction.KeyValueExtraction

  • @Component
public class KeyValueExtraction
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to extract the document level fields using key value extraction. Update the extracted data as a document level fields to the batch.xml file.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ephesoft
    See Also:
